<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="468" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1435,289,350]" pageId="1" pageNumber="468">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,286,289,314]" pageId="1" pageNumber="468">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name of the new genus is derived from the Latin words 
<emphasis box="[1047,1105,289,313]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="468">short</emphasis>
(short) and 
<emphasis box="[1258,1327,290,313]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="468">crown</emphasis>
(crown), indicating the shape of its crown.
</paragraph>
